msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "The PC-FX mouse is a two-button ball mouse released in 1994. It is supported by strategy games like Farland Story FX and Power DoLLS FX."
msgstr "PC-FX Mouse je dvoutlačítková kuličková myš vydaná v roce 1994. Podporují ji strategické hry jako Farland Story FX a Power DoLLS FX."

